extendedInfo.description: GoSMSPro Metallic HalloweenREAD THE FOLLOWING CAREFULLY!I would very much like to receive a rating from you even if you are dissattisfied and want to give it a low rating. If the latter is the case please explain why so I can see if I can improve upon it. Thank you very much :DLook at "more from developer" for other colors.https://market.android.com/developer?pub=Ry4ndroidThis app is a theme and will only work with GO SMS PRO. You need to have this application installed first and then install this theme. You can apply the theme from within the GO SMS PRO app. You cannot open the application on its own.If you feel adventurous, and are not satisfied with the text colours I chose, you can change them in the advance mode of GO SMS.I created this theme with the tools provided by the GO SMS PRO team and should work if GO SMS PRO works on your phone.To apply this theme:Launch GO SMS Pro, use the theme option (general tab) browse for this theme ("installed themes" tab), select it to apply/rate.I will try and assist where possible, but please bear in mind that I did not create GO SMS PRO and can only assist with theme related issues. You are welcome to do any requests. I will try and create other colours in the future. You can contact me at Ry4ndroid@gmail.comKeywords:GO SMS Pro theme gosmstheme theme sms gingerbread Ry4ndroid Green Black Purple Orange Halloween Metal Steel Metallic
